name: Corneo's Covering Breasts TI Embed - Two Hands Version
description:
This is a Textual Inversion embedding to induce a pose where the character is covering their breasts with the palms of their hands. I've other embeds for a one-arm version and arms crossed version.

By default it really wants to generate gigantic breasts(!) and small hands, so prompt for your desired breast size.

Example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
